------------------------
Welcome to Good Ovening!
------------------------

Installation:

   * This project is currently a simple source distribution on
     GitHub. Check it out here:

     > git clone https://github.com/mattp/good_ovening.git

   * The web-crawling tool Scrapy (http://scrapy.org/) must be
     pre-installed on your system:

     > pip install scrapy

Running good_ovening:

   * Currently basic execution of the crawler is done using:

     > ./run.sh

   * The crawler will not run twice on the same day unless you remove
     the corresponding XML file in the xml directory.